{
  "title": "Smart Packing: Carry-On Essentials for 7-Day Trips",
  "description": "Master packing light with a modular capsule system built for comfort and utility. This post lists fabrics, multi-use gear, compression strategies, and a quick wash-and-refresh routine to keep outfits fresh. Includes a printable packing checklist.",
  "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504215680853-026ed2a45def?w=1200&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop",
