  "title": "Mindful Leadership: Practices to Build Resilient Teams",
  "description": "Practical leadership practices that cultivate psychological safety, focus, and resilience. Topics include intentional listening, clarity in role expectations, and rituals that reconnect teams across distributed settings. Includes a simple 5-minute daily check-in template.",
